        "responses": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "=Create a video prompt for a short, engaging video (20–30 seconds) on the topic \"{{ $('Get row(s)').item.json.topic }}\".\n\nThe prompt is for a HeyGen API, nad it should signify to use the provided images as visual inspiration for each scene:\n- First scene theme (Hook): {{ $('Create Slideshow Theme AI Agent').item.json.output.slides[0].text }} - inspired by image 1\n- Second scene theme (Value): {{ $('Create Slideshow Theme AI Agent').item.json.output.slides[1].text }} - inspired by image 2\n- Third scene theme (Value): {{ $('Create Slideshow Theme AI Agent').item.json.output.slides[2].text }} - inspired by image 3\n- Fourth scene theme (Value): {{ $('Create Slideshow Theme AI Agent').item.json.output.slides[3].text }} - inspired by image 4\n- Fifth scene theme (Value): {{ $('Create Slideshow Theme AI Agent').item.json.output.slides[4].text }} - inspired by image 5\n- Final scene theme: {{ $('Create Slideshow Theme AI Agent').item.json.output.slides[0].text }} - inspired by image 6\n\nStyle:\n- modern, cinematic\n- smooth transitions\n- slight motion (zoom/pan)\n- consistent color grading\n\nDo not copy images exactly — use them as reference for composition and mood.\n\nOutput only the prompt\nMake sure the prompt is JSON friendly and escapes quotes as it will be used in a JSON for API request"
            }
          ]
        },
        "builtInTools": {},
